text: Hi all :wave: I've been on this group for a while now and have picked up some excellent tips from you all, and thought it was probably time for me to introduce myself! I lead on content marketing for a B2B SaaS company called Beauhurst. We track fast-growing companies in the UK and provide all kinds of company data to all kinds of industries. I regularly write about startup, investment and VC trends, and  would be keen to connect with anyone else who writes in this space! :hugging_face:
